comment: Zeller (CHA) sets the screen on Rondo (SAC) and gives him room to avoid the contact. The two players make incidental contact.
Lin (CHA) and Belinelli (SAC) briefly engage and separate away from the ball.
Gay (SAC) makes contact with Batum (CHA) with his left arm and the contact affects his RSBQ in the backcourt.
Zeller (CHA) sets the screen on Rondo (SAC) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Zeller (CHA) maintains legal guarding position and absorbs the contact from Gay (SAC) as he defends the driving shot attempt.
Koufos (SAC) sets the screen on Lin (CHA) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Zeller (CHA) sets the screen on Rondo (SAC) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Gay (SAC) sets the screen on Batum (CHA) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Gay (SAC) and Williams (CHA) briefly engage and Gay makes a legal move to the basket prior to catching the alley-oop.
After communicating with the Replay Center, the ruling on the court of a successful basket by Gay (SAC) prior to time expiring was upheld.
Zeller (CHA) sets the screen on Rondo (SAC) and gives him room to avoid the contact. The contact between the two players after the screen is incidental.
Koufos (SAC) dislodges Zeller (CHA), affecting his ability to retrieve the rebound.
Zeller (CHA) sets the screen on Gay (SAC) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Belinelli (SAC) makes contact with Lin's (CHA) arm that affects his shot attempt.
Koufos (SAC) obtains a legal guarding position on the drive to the basket by Zeller (CHA).
The contact between Zeller (CHA) and Koufos (SAC) is incidental. Koufos then bumps his teammate Collison (SAC) and causes him to fall to the floor.
Gay (SAC) makes a legal move when he rolls toward the basket with Walker (CHA) defending him.
Gay (SAC) makes incidental contact with Walker (CHA) and does not dislodge him during rebounding.
Rondo (SAC) commits a take foul on Zeller (CHA).
The contact between Belinelli (SAC) and Zeller (CHA) is incidental as Belinelli attempts to defend Lin's (CHA) driving shot attempt.
Koufos (SAC) and Lin (CHA) make incidental contact with one another as Koufos rolls to the basket.
RHH shows that Rondo (SAC) makes contact with the ball as he attempts to strip it from behind on Lin's (CHA) drive to the basket.
Koufos (SAC) obtains a legal guarding position and jumps vertically as he defends Lin's (CHA) driving shot attempt.
[Observable in production angle] Walker (CHA) legally contests Belinelli's (SAC) jump shot attempt. After the shot is released, Belinelli's flails his arm and makes contact with Walker's face.
Gay (SAC) maintains legal guarding position and cleanly blocks Kaminsky's (CHA) driving layup attempt.
Zeller (CHA) makes contact with Koufos' (SAC) arm that affects his shot attempt.
Walker (CHA) cleanly strips the ball from Gay (SAC). Gay is allowed to return to the floor because the ball was loose.
Koufos (SAC) commits a take foul on Walker (CHA).
Rondo (SAC) commits a take foul on Lin (CHA).
